<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>오류 발생</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 80px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .button {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>⚠ 오류가 발생했습니다</h1>

{{#errorMessage}}
    <p>{{errorMessage}}</p>
{{/errorMessage}}

{{^errorMessage}}
    <p>예상치 못한 오류가 발생했습니다. 나중에 다시 시도해주세요.</p>
{{/errorMessage}}

<form action="/main" method="get">
    <button class="button" type="submit">메인으로 돌아가기</button>
</form>
</body>
</html>